!! !!Other consonant rules 
! =====================

"Final C Deletion"
!! __@RULENAME@__  
Cx:0 <=> _ (Dummy:) %^CDEL: ;
	where Cx in ( b d g s h ) ; ! JW: added h (riebe/riehpeha); what about j (båtsoj/buhtsu)??

! !!€ riehpeh^WG^CDEL
! !!€ rie0be000
! !!€ biednag^WG^CDEL
! !!€ bie0na000


"Final devoicing"
!! __@RULENAME@__  
Cx:Cy <=> _ .#. ;
    where Cx in ( b2 d2 g2 )
          Cy in ( p  t  k  )
          matched ; ! JW: removed pair h2:j (not sure what it refers to)

! !!€ árrad2
! !!€ árrat
! !!€ árrad2e
! !!€ árrade
! !!€ unneb2
! !!€ unnep


"Word Final Simplification in -st" !st->s (eg. elat) variation (descriptive, not normative)
!! __@RULENAME@__  
t2:0 <=> s _ .#. ;

! !!€ burist2
! !!€ buris0


"Fricative Auslautverhärtung" !variation (eg. dim-suffix) (descriptive, not normative) (sj - tj word-finally)
!! __@RULENAME@__  
s:t <=> _ j2: .#. ;




