!! ! raising second syllable's vowel

"E to I in V2 before j-suffixes" ! guolle -> gulij
!! __@RULENAME@__  
e:i <=> Vow:+ Cns:+ _ (Dummy:) %^IJ:0 ; !guolle<->gulij juällge<->julgij sábme<->sämij

!! ! metaphony

"Default VH" !regressive vowel height assimilation in V1 with i/u in V2" ! á:ä a:i ä:e å:u ^O:0
!! __@RULENAME@__  
Vx:Vy <=> [.#.|Cns|#|i] _ Cns:+ \Vow: [:i|:u] ; !Cns:* Dummy:* %>:* ; !guolle<->gulij juällge<->julgij sábme<->sämij båtsoj<->buhtsu (last one w/o morpheme boundary!)
    where Vx in ( á a ä å )
          Vy in ( ä i e u )
          matched ; 

